Dorothy Bellew https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Bellew 0 Dorothy Bellew (8 August 1891 – 29 October 1973) was an English actress. She appeared in around sixty films during the silent era, including the title role in Lorna Doone (1912). Dorothy_Bellew ( 8_August_1891 – 29_October_1973 ) was an_English_actress .
